'''Pascale Lamche''' (yavutse Nyakanga 1960), ni [[Ubufaransa|Umufaransa]] -Umukinnyi wa firime [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] <ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1088150/</ref>. Azwi nk'umuyobozi wa firime nyinshi zizwi cyane harimo ''Stalingrad'', ''Black Diamond'', ''Pakisitani Zindabad'', ''Ubwiza bw'Abafaransa'', ''Ushinjwa # 1: Nelson Mandela'', ''Sophiatown'' na ''Winnie''<ref>https://africa.film/winnie-a-pascale-lamche-documentary/</ref> .  Usibye gukora firime, ni na producer, umwanditsi akaba n'umukinnyi wa sinema.<ref>https://womensmediacenter.com/profile/pascale-lamche</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Yabonye icyiciro cya mbere cyicyubahiro BA impamyabumenyi yamateka ya none yakuye muri Kaminuza ya Sussex na Sorbonne .<ref>https://dokincubator.net/3rd-workshop-session-2021/</ref> Yatangiye umwuga wa firime i Londere mu kigo cyigenga cya firime, Cinema Action, akora mu kigega cy’iburayi cyandika mu 1989<ref>https://www.theelephant.info/features/2018/06/14/mother-of-the-nation-saint-and-sinner/</ref>. Icyakora, nyuma yaje kwimukira i Paris gushinga ICONE, umushinga wo gukorana na firime na televiziyo. Yagize amahirwe yo gukorera i Londere na Paris nk'umuproducer n'umuyobozi wigenga<ref>https://womensmediacenter.com/profile/pascale-lamche#:~:text=Pascale%20Lamche%20is%20an%20award,down%20Apartheid%20in%20South%20Africa.</ref>. Aherekeza hamwe na societe ''ntoya'' yo gukora documentaire. Nyuma yinjiye muri 'La Cie Phares et Balises' maze aba umuyobozi wa International Co-Productions for Kamera Continentales<ref>https://www.news24.com/news24/SouthAfrica/News/director-of-winnie-documentary-believes-her-film-has-sparked-important-discussions-20180416</ref>. 

Muri 2017, yakoze filime documentaire ''Winnie'', ivuga ku buzima bwa Winnie Madikizela-Mandela n'urugamba rwe rwo gusenya Apartheid muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo.   Iyi filime yerekanwe mu rwego rwo kwerekana iserukiramuco ry'uburenganzira bwa muntu 2019.<ref>https://cambridgegirltalk.com/2018/01/12/feminist-filmmaking-and-winnie-a-conversation-with-pascale-lamche/</ref>  Muri uwo mwaka, yatsindiye igihembo cy'umuyobozi mwiza wa documentaire mpuzamahanga muri Sundance Festival<ref>https://www.sundance.org/projects/winnie</ref> . Muri Mata 2018, Lamche yasobanuye ko uwahoze ari minisitiri w’umutekano n’umutekano  Sydney Mufamadi mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru<ref>https://alt-africa.com/2018/02/18/interview-with-director-pascale-lamche-winnie-2016/</ref>. 

